                            <apex:param value="{!quote.fm_TotalLoanAmount__c - quote.CapitalDefermentAmount__c}" />
                        </apex:outputText>
                    </th>
                    <th></th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>캐피탈 부가세 유예금 (Capital VAT Deferment)</th>
